Class JMGUI

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.awt.Component
      • java.awt.Container
        • java.awt.Window
          • java.awt.Frame

              • JMGUI
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible, javax.swing.RootPaneContainer, javax.swing.WindowConstants

    public class JMGUI
extends javax.swing.JFrame
    The class JMGUI functions as the view component of the Johnny Moves Model-View-Component application. It consists of all of the Johnny Moves Application's Graphical User Interface, aside from the JMOpen class.
